Username: This is a text field with no character limits.  The system will validate to see whether this same user name exists. If no exact match is found, the record will not be inserted and the row will be marked invalid. This is a required field and if missing, the row will be marked invalid.  NOTE: To input multiple property code assignments to one user, a separate row for each property must be created with both columns filled out prior to upload.
PropertyCode: The Property Code field is an alphanumeric field only and is limited to 50 characters.  This field should be checked for an exact match.  If no exact match exists, the row will be marked invalid.  This is a required field for this upload.  If missing, the row will be marked invalid.
